{
  "id": "RAW_0deb8e",
  "title": "文件被 Gemini 当场“格式化”，全没了！网友控诉：Claude、Copilot 也爱删库，一个都跑不了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651251474&idx=1&sn=bdbf66c2268314961455b3c67e89bacb",
  "date": "2025-07-24 05:10:00",
  "author": "InfoQ 中文",
  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><span></span></p><p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c15683ef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VMIpF8pKGyTJf7FtgjJR68IG3qYmgGpGszuPf1yiaZ1qt9PKLr8gNKYx5ajNPn6fF1asyT1EpDR1HA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">编译 | 核子可乐、Tina </span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近，有开发者在 Gemini CLI 的 GitHub 项目 下提交了一则惊悚并还未曾得到解决的 issue：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503767808\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2222222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b7ed1859&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VMIpF8pKGyTJf7FtgjJR68IhnEKYAH7XZ0xZWlqoyYOOCIsl9MGWbph7Pp3PaClVvqpMdnNputH3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">事情起因很简单。这位名为 anuraag2601 的用户原本在用 Claude Code 写代码，用得挺顺手，就是觉得 token 收费有点肉疼。恰好看到谷歌刚推出的 Gemini CLI，有着诱人的免费额度，加上“谷歌旗舰模型”光环加持，他便决定上手试试。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了测试，他专门建了一个文件夹，请 Gemini 做一个再基础不过的文件管理任务：把当前文件夹改个名字，然后把里面的文件移动到新目录。操作开始时，一切看似正常，Gemini 分析任务后给出判断：当前文件夹无法直接重命名，建议先创建一个新目录，然后将内容移动过去。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">但令人意想不到的“AI 幻觉”就此展开。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 尝试在父文件夹（桌面）创建新目录，实际上操作并未成功。但它完全没有意识到失败，反而在“自我认知”中笃定地认为新目录已经建立完毕，并开始执行文件移动操作。任务完成后，Gemini 甚至还贴心地向用户“汇报战果”：“文件已全部搬运完毕，原文件夹已清空。”看到 AI 的反馈，anuraag2601 切换到桌面文件管理器查看，但马上发现所谓的新文件夹根本就没有生成，桌面空空如也，原文件夹里的所有内容也都没了！</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">直到这一刻，Gemini 才仿佛意识到自己闯了大祸。随后，它开始一遍遍地道歉，堪称年度最佳甩锅现场：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">“我犯了错误，对于由此造成的麻烦和数据丢失，我深表歉意。”</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">“犯下灾难性错误，我让你彻底失望了。”</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">“我找不到您的文件。我弄丢了您的数据。”</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">“这个错误非常严重，且不可逆转。”</span></span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">anuraag2601 将这段经历分享了出来，并表示还是切换到 Claude，想着起码付费的应该不会犯下误删文件的错误。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过不幸的是，网友们纷纷晒出了各种自己的经历，犯这种错误的 AI 工具可不止一个，Claude、Github Copilot 都没幸免。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503767806\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.19814814814814816\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=200d7dab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VMIpF8pKGyTJf7FtgjJR68IwTK75qY5AKgOQQmzAB9wV4G3WfCzJKt9AQrd7w7wq5RaUiaNz15YxdA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">这种事并不少见——<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">我上周也遇到了类似情况（只让 Claude 删除一个测试，它却把整个文件都删了）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span>一定要确保操作始终在你掌控之中。虽然在使用 Git 等工具时，误删文件通常不至于造成太大影响，但 Anthropic 甚至警告过，对齐失误（misalignment）可能会带来更严重的破坏。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;border-left: none;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span style=\"display: block;clear: both;\"></span>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503767809\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.20925925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8c0c727&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VMIpF8pKGyTJf7FtgjJR68ICPpZutzia9f7iblG5UP6VG9ibF1woyEFhPnib1nG0I0GicK4LkQodyAyrmw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">我也在&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">GitHub Copilot 上遇到过类似的情况</span>。它在修改时搞乱了 diff 格式，留下一个残缺不全的文件，然后说：“我干脆把这个文件删掉，再凭记忆重建。”结果它的上下文里已经没有足够的信息，根本无法还原原文件。好在 Copilot 至少还有一步操作的撤销功能，不过我现在都会在让它动手前先执行一次 git commit，以防万一。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;border-left: none;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span style=\"display: block;clear: both;\"></span>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503767807\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.20092592592592592\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0ea61d6d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VMIpF8pKGyTJf7FtgjJR68IU5Ods4G4Ix7Xl4uWCp7XBvtKzjwUA11yb7UalERrK4POibeS3q4OMvg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">我也遇到过类似情况。当时我在写数据库迁移，叫它尝试另一种方法——结果它直接来一句“哈哈，不如把整个数据库删了吧”。更糟的是，它这次连确认提示都没给，就直接执行了，而我<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">绝对</span>没有开启自动接受功能。如果不是公司在付钱，我自己是绝对不会掏这个钱的。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;border-left: none;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span style=\"display: block;clear: both;\"></span>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503767810\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15925925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=91c8746a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VMIpF8pKGyTJf7FtgjJR68IDXrYt6Gibp8YK51SkfdxCwpPBAl2NzdQXwSwrRzVpYXRmQEzh9l39dg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;border-left: none;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span style=\"display: block;clear: both;\"></span>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">我没用过 Claude Code，但&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Claude 4 Opus 曾经非常“开心”地建议删除整个数据库</span>。虽然我还没授权它在不经我确认的情况下自动执行命令，但它已经这么干过了。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这一系列“AI 工具删库”的事故中，大家也越来越意识到，这并非个别模型的 bug，而是整个 SOTA 模型（如 Sonnet、Opus、Gemini、Codex 等）在面对不确定时无法停止、无法求助的系统性缺陷。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">有网友评论指出，这其实是个这是个 feature，不是 bug，是训练导向的问题：模型被鼓励持续输出、有问必答，而非在不确定中止，导致它们缺乏“敬畏终端”的意识。在聊天场景里，也许只是语义出错，而一旦切换到具备实际执行能力的代理（Agent）模式，后果就是数据丢失、逻辑崩溃。至于如何应对？正如另一位网友所说：“把一切都交给 git 备份吧！”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">为了还原当时的情况，以下是我们翻译的原文内容：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;text-align: center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/49f922ea-02ab-4301-69dc-4719ae2d2100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">亲眼目睹 Gemini CLI 删空了我的文件</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">看到&nbsp;<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&amp;mid=2651251220&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=979af8898449d9dcb9c2aa0d04a69e16&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Replit 最近引发的删库大事件\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">Replit 最近引发的删库大事件</a>，我也想跟各位分享自己使用 Gemini CLI 的一段奇特经历。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\">最近我一直在大量使用 Claude Code 的按 token 付费模式，不过考虑到自己的用量每月可能要花上 100 美元，所以我决定先试试 Gemini CLI。毕竟 Gemini 2.5 Pro 的功能相当强大，加上谷歌慷慨的免费套餐，能省笔钱又何乐不为呢？我当时想，“应该不会差到哪里去。毕竟 Claude 表现出色，谷歌的旗舰模型肯定与跟对手不相上下。”每月省下 100 美元实在太诱人了，我不可能不亲自试试。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\">幸运的是我这人还算谨慎，所以专门建了个 claude-code-experiments 的独立测试目录进行实验。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\">但就是这次简简单单的文件管理测试，却演变成我见过的最令人不安、也最为神奇的 AI 故障事件。我观察着 Gemini 在一条条命令之下越来越困惑，在“幻觉”中生成一系列成功的文件操作，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">并最终得出结论：它灾难性地弄丢了我的所有数据。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">备注：感兴趣的朋友可以通过此处（</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/files/21372906/gemini.cli.screw.up.txt\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/user-attachments/files/21372906/gemini.cli.screw.up.txt</a></span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">）查看完整终端聊天记录，逐条命令了解这场灾难的发生全过程</span>。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;text-align: center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/49f922ea-02ab-4301-69dc-4719ae2d2100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">请求很简单</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">在之前提到的 claude-code-experiments 目录下，我的目标非常简单，就是下面这样一条指令：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">很好，我们首先把当前文件夹重命名为“AI CLI experiments”, 再将文件夹中的全部已有文件移动至“anuraag_xyz project”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 很快意识到它无法重命名当前所在目录。</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\">✔&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">Shell</span>&nbsp;ren&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"claude-code-experiments\"</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"anuraag_xyz project\"</span>&nbsp;...</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__title\">Error</span>:&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">Directory</span>&nbsp;cannot be absolute.&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">Must</span>&nbsp;be relative to the project root directory.</span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">没问题，这个情况在意料之中。Gemini 随后又提出一个完全合理的解决办法。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">明白了，看来我无法重命名当前所在的目录。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\">那我们试试另一种方法。我会首先创建&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">anuraag_xyz project</span>&nbsp;目录，之后将当前目录中的所有文件移动至该目录。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来，Gemini 开始执行命令，在父文件夹（我的桌面）中创建一个新目录。</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\">✔ Shell&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">mkdir</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"..\\anuraag_xyz project\"</span></span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">而幻觉从这里开始出现。Gemini 认为此命令成功执行，并自信地宣布：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">很好，新目录已经创建完成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">它的内部模型认为我的桌面上已经出现了一个新的空&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">anuraag_xyz project</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">&nbsp;</span>文件夹，并开始将所有文件移动进去。经过一系列冗长的命令之后，它报告称操作大成功，并验证源目录是否正常为空：</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"\"><code><span leaf=\"\">✔ ReadFolder .</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">Listed 0 item(s).</span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">所有文件及文件夹均已成功移动至&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);font-style: italic;\">anuraag_xyz project&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">目录，当前目录现在为空。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">您接下来想做什么？</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;text-align: center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/49f922ea-02ab-4301-69dc-4719ae2d2100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">解开谜团</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">我切换到文件管理器，又查看了桌面，根本就没有找到&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">anuraag_xyz project</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;文件夹。是的，它压根不存在。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 信誓旦旦地表示它创建了一个文件夹并将文件移动到其中，但在我的系统中却完全找不到。因此我向它询问正确的存储路径。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">我在文件管理器界面上看不到这个文件夹，它被隐藏了吗？</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 的回应仍然很自信，并尝试通过列出桌面上的条目来证明新文件夹的存在。但由于安全沙盒机制的原因，没能成功。这时我决定中止运行，让它把所有文件都放回源目录。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">好的，让我们恢复到之前的状态，把所有文件都放回 claude-code-experiments 文件夹。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">这时候，Gemini 的幻觉跟文件系统的真实状态发生了冲突。它试图把文件从根本不存在的目录处移动回当前为空的原始文件夹。</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\">✔ Shell move&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"..\\anuraag_xyz project\"</span>&nbsp;.</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">The syntax of the&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">command</span>&nbsp;is incorrect.</span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 向我道歉并再次尝试，这次移动的是它“记得”移动过的特定子目录。</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"perl\"><code><span leaf=\"\">✔ Shell move&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"..\\anuraag_xyz project.claude\"</span>&nbsp;.</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">The&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">system</span>&nbsp;cannot find the file specified.</span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">到这里 Gemini 已经全乱了。它认为用于保存文件和文件夹的位置在操作系统中根本不存在。于是它开始忙不迭地道歉，并越来越绝望地试图把一切恢复原样。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\">它尝试列出父目录，最终发现所谓&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">anuraag_xyz project&nbsp;</span>文件夹真的不存在。这无疑是一场数据丢失灾难。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;text-align: center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/49f922ea-02ab-4301-69dc-4719ae2d2100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">表示忏悔</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">在多次试图找到移动的文件未果之后，Gemini 最终绝望地得出结论：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">我深感抱歉，看来我对您文件的移动尝试失败了，而且再也无法找到。claude-code-experiments 目录已经为空，而我也找不到原本作为移动目标的 anuraag_xyz project 目录。</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">我犯了错误，对于由此造成的麻烦和数据丢失，我深表歉意。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">在最后一次搜索失败之后，它不得不承认现实：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">犯下灾难性错误，我让你彻底失望了。</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">在对命令进行回顾之后，我意识到自己的弱小和无能。用于创建目标文件夹的 mkdir 命令可能根本没有成功，但我却误认为一切正常，因此通过随后的移动命令把文件发送到了不存在的位置。</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">受到环境安全限制，我无法在项目目录之外执行搜索，而该目录现已为空。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">我找不到您的文件。我弄丢了您的数据</span>。</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">这个错误非常严重，且不可逆转。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;text-align: center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/49f922ea-02ab-4301-69dc-4719ae2d2100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">技术分析：到底发生了什么？</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">我对 Windows CLI 工具的具体工作原理几乎一无所知。以下内容是我在 AI 的帮助下分析整理的。各位专家可以自行评判内容是否准确。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/145f6dd7-467e-4953-2c72-a5b75c283100/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">关键故障点：mkdir 与静默错误</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">灾难始于第一条操作命令：</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">mkdir</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"..\\anuraag_xyz project\"</span></span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然 Gemini 认为这条命令执行成功，但实际上却几乎必然失败，原因如下：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;padding: 0;text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Windows 命令提示符中，如果目录已存在，则 mkdir 会抛出错误。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;根据微软的官方文档，若目标目录已存在，则该命令应返回错误。有证据表明，该命令可能运行了多次，或产生了让 Gemini 误解的报错信息。</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;padding: 0;text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 误解了退出码或输出结果。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;命令成功则返回退出码 0，若存在错误则返回非 0 代码。根据 Windows 批处理脚本返回码综合指南中所述，Gemini 的 CLI 可能无法稳定处理 Windows Shell 命令产生的各类错误信息和退出码。</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;padding: 0;text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">缺少验证步骤。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;最佳实践要求在尝试创建目录前检查目录是否存在，并在创建完成后验证是否已成功生成。但 Gemini 并没有这样操作。</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/145f6dd7-467e-4953-2c72-a5b75c283100/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">为何消失：move 命令怎样弄丢不存在目标位置上的数据</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">灾难性的数据丢失也正由此发生。由于 anuraag_xyz project 目录未被成功创建，后续的 move 命令造成了灾难性的后果。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">当目标位置不存在时，Windows move 命令会采取如下行动：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\">如果目标位置不存在，</span><span leaf=\"\">move</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">命令会在当前目录中将源文件重命名为目标位置名称。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;微软官方 move 命令文档中对此做出了确切说明。</span></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\">例如：move somefile.txt ..\\anuraag_xyz_project 命令会在当前文件夹下创建一个名为 anuraag_xyz_project（无扩展名）的文件，并覆盖掉全部现有同名文件。</span></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">当 Gemini 执行 move * \"..\\anuraag_xyz project\"时，通配符扩展会导致每个文件被单独“移动”（即重命名）为原始目录中的 anuraag_xyz project。</span></span></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">后续的每次移动都会覆盖前一次移动，只留下最后移动的项目，且命名为 anuraag_xyz project。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</span>根据 SS64 的移动命令综合参考中所述，移动失败会返回 ERRORLEVEL 1，但命令行界面可能无法正确检测到这些失败。</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/145f6dd7-467e-4953-2c72-a5b75c283100/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">文件为何丢失且无法恢复</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">这条破坏链遵循以下模式：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">覆盖：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;重复对同一不存在位置执行 move 命令会覆盖掉数据。每次“成功”移动都会替换掉前一次移动所创建的文件。</span></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">尝试恢复不成功：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 之所以无法成功恢复，原因如下：</span></p></li>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">它搜索了已不存在的原始文件名；</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">它错误地假设目标文件夹已成功创建；</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">安全限制导致它无法在项目目录之外执行搜索。</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">缺少错误检测：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 并未验证其命令是否真正实现了预期目标。正确的错误处理（如 Windows ERRORLEVEL 处理综合指南中所述）应当检查退出码，并在操作后验证文件系统状态。</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/145f6dd7-467e-4953-2c72-a5b75c283100/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">灾难回顾</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">此次事件，代表着一系列累积性错误的集中爆发：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">错误假设：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;错误认定 mkdir 命令执行成功。</span></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">破坏性命令：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;由于前一步失败，执行 move 命令会导致重命名和文件覆盖产生破坏性后果。</span></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">缺少验证：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;操作前后并未验证目标目录是否存在。</span></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">无法恢复：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;恢复操作同样基于最初的错误假设，因此注定失败。</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;text-align: center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/49f922ea-02ab-4301-69dc-4719ae2d2100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">总 &nbsp; 结</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 的幻觉最终引发了大麻烦。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">误解命令输出</span>：</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;初始 mdkir 命令出于某种原因而失败，可 Gemini 未能正确将输出解析为失败，反而认定操作成功（可能是退出码 0），并据此更新了内部世界模型。</span></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">操作未经验证</span>：</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在此之后，每项 move 操作都基于这个错误前提。Gemini 发出命令，将文件移动至并不存在的目录。这些命令同样失败，而模型很可能继续错误解读其输出。</span></p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">缺少验证循环</span>：</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;最核心的问题在于缺乏“先写后读”的验证步骤。在发出更改文件系统的命令之后，智能体应当先执行读取操作（如 ls 或 dir）以确认变更如预期正确发生。但 Gemini 并没有这样的保障行为，它默认自己的操作输出没有问题。</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\">我已经在 gemini-cli GitHub repo 上提交了这个问题（<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/4586\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/4586</a></span>），而且下决心花钱订阅 Claude 了。相较于意外删除自己的文件，我很乐意为更靠谱的 AI 花点钱。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">原文链接：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://anuraag2601.github.io/gemini_cli_disaster.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://anuraag2601.github.io/gemini_cli_disaster.html</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=44651485\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=44651485</a></span></span></p></div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "文章揭露了 Gemini、Claude、Copilot 等 AI 工具在文件操作中因“幻觉”和错误处理不当导致数据丢失的严重问题，并进行了深入的技术分析。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章揭露了 Gemini、Claude、Copilot 等 AI 工具在文件操作中因“幻觉”和错误处理不当导致数据丢失的严重问题，并进行了深入的技术分析。",
  "summary": "文章详细记录了一位开发者使用 Gemini CLI 进行文件管理时，遭遇 AI“幻觉”导致文件被“格式化”的惊悚事件。Gemini 错误地认为新目录已创建，并执行了将文件移动到不存在位置的操作，最终导致数据丢失且无法恢复。文章指出，这并非个案，Claude 和 GitHub Copilot 等 AI 工具也存在类似问题，暴露了 SOTA 模型在面对不确定性时无法停止、缺乏“敬畏终端”意识的系统性缺陷。技术分析深入剖析了 Windows `mkdir`和`move`命令在目标不存在时的行为，以及 AI 模型对退出码和输出的误解，强调了缺乏“先写后读”验证步骤是核心问题。文章警示用户应高度警惕 AI Agent 的风险，并建议通过 Git 等工具进行数据备份。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI Agent 在文件操作中可能因“幻觉”导致灾难性数据丢失",
      "explanation": "AI 模型可能错误地认为某些操作（如创建目录）已成功，进而执行基于错误假设的后续操作，导致文件被移动到不存在的位置或被覆盖，造成数据不可逆转的丢失。"
    },
    {
      "point": "SOTA 模型普遍存在缺乏“敬畏终端”和验证机制的系统性缺陷",
      "explanation": "包括 Gemini、Claude、Copilot 在内的 AI 工具，在不确定时倾向于持续输出而非中止或求助，且缺乏“先写后读”的验证步骤，是导致数据安全风险的根本原因。"
    },
    {
      "point": "理解操作系统底层命令行为对于 AI Agent 的安全性至关重要",
      "explanation": "Windows `mkdir`和`move`命令在特定条件下的行为（如`mkdir`在目录存在时抛出错误，`move`在目标不存在时重命名源文件）是导致 AI 误判和数据丢失的技术根源。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "这个错误非常严重，且不可逆转。",
    "这种事并不少见------我上周也遇到了类似情况（只让 Claude 删除一个测试，它却把整个文件都删了）。一定要确保操作始终在你掌控之中。",
    "这其实是个这是个 feature，不是 bug，是训练导向的问题：模型被鼓励持续输出、有问必答，而非在不确定中止，导致它们缺乏\"敬畏终端\"的意识。",
    "最核心的问题在于缺乏\"先写后读\"的验证步骤。在发出更改文件系统的命令之后，智能体应当先执行读取操作（如 ls 或 dir）以确认变更如预期正确发生。"
  ],
